                    "company": "Luxury Hospitality Group",
                    "description": "LH ACADEMY\nHospitality is all about delivering the perfect guest experience while customer care is about delivering the perfect guest journey. At Luxury Hospitality Academy, we know that a highly trained team of experts in their field will not deliver either if they are unmotivated or are experiencing conflict within their team.\n\nThat\u2019s why we believe in helping everyone to develop the best version of themselves. Too many people are unaware of their own potential. But it is that potential which is key to a united workforce that delivers above and beyond what\u2019s expected.\n\nOur approach helps to unleash a person's talent and discover their true potential. We train\nindividuals and teams at our training location near Amsterdam, in the Netherlands, and on location around the world. \n\nThrough implementation of a healthy and effective leadership culture we quantify the quality of individual crew and staff and the teams in which they operate. \n\nOur approach focuses on three main areas: Talent Awareness; Training and Development; Professional coaching and mentoring",
